profile:
At Grants Concrete we are a full service contractor offering all aspects of a professional concrete installation. Like any construction project there are key elements that are necessary for a quality concrete project to not only look good but stand the test of time. Elements such as proper grade preparation, drainage, reinforcements, concrete mix design, formwork and placing techniques need to be implemented to provide a lasting installation. We are experienced and equipped to provide all of these elements in a friendly and helpful manner. In addition to providing a quality project our goal is to provide a service you would be pleased to recommend.

Based out of Maple Ridge BC we service all of Greater Vancouver and the Fraser Valley. We are available for larger projects in locations throughout British Columbia.

We are pleased to provide references upon request.

We carry 2 million liability insurance and Worksafe BC.

see us on the wen at http://grantsconcrete.com
